cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.CL

This paper is about action recognition in videos, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses training models and loss functions, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper introduces a new dataset, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses interpreting models, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) or natural language processing (cs.CL) if the models are used for captioning or generating descriptions of videos.
